   <head>Lirica latina - Lirica XXVI</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Quod semper vino madidus, somnique benignus,</l>
     <l n="2">securus pendis nil, nisi quod placeat,</l>
     <l n="3">laetitia frueris nimirum, Bacche, perenni,</l>
     <l n="4">exarat et frontem nulla senecta tuam.</l>
     <l n="5">Sic quicumque pedem tua per vestigia ponet,</l>
     <l n="6">exiget in multa saecula longa rosa.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
